title: A handmade investigation to test the ISA_API
description: This investigation was made by hand, following the JSON schemas provided at https://isa-specs.readthedocs.io/en/latest/isajson.html#format and the examples BII-I-1, BII-S-3, and BII-S-7. Fields for information that is not currently recorded in FAIRDOM-SEEK are left blank. The schema material_schema.json is modified so that the Type is set to String and does not expect the values Extract Name or Labeled Extract Name
